public class MilitaryAlpinistEquipment extends KI.Chaus.Lab3.AlpinistEquipment implements KI.Chaus.Lab3.MilitaryAlpinistEquipmentInterface
This class represents military alpinist equipment and extends the AlpinistEquipment class. It provides mechanisms for correct functioning specific to military equipment. It also implements the MilitaryEquipment interface.
